      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Conclusion, when N=100, and the distribution is normal, the mean is more efficient than the median.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Change assumptions, from N to t-distribution\n"
